(2, 'Footer', 'About', 'slavery-and-human-trafficking-statement', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">March 2023</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller Limited (\"Unipuller\") remains steadfast in its commitment to combat modern slavery and human trafficking. This statement provides additional insight into the comprehensive measures taken by Unipuller to ensure ethical practices throughout its operations and supply chain.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Expanded Introduction:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller, a global business with a significant presence in the UK, specializes in digital products designed to enhance merchant visibility. Our diverse product range, which includes online directories, websites, search and display products, and analytic tools, necessitates a complex supply chain spanning countries like India and the Philippines. These locations host various critical functions, such as customer services, production facilities, and IT services.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Holistic Ethical Approach:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller\'s commitment to ethical business practices is encapsulated in the Unipuller Code of Ethics. This code not only emphasizes the right of every individual to be treated with honesty and respect but also articulates our dedication to providing a safe and healthy work environment. Beyond the fundamental principles, the Code stipulates that suppliers must not only meet but exceed minimum wage guidelines, adhere to working hour limits, and abstain from employing child labor.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To ensure the widespread understanding and adherence to these principles, our Compliance Team oversees the comprehensive training of all new employees in the Code of Ethics, fostering a culture of responsibility and awareness.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>International Standards for Suppliers:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to our internal Code of Ethics, Unipuller mandates that suppliers adhere to a distinct Code of Ethics. This external code aligns with statutory requirements and international standards set forth in the UN Universal Declaration of Human Rights and the International Labour Organization Conventions. This duallayered approach underscores our commitment to holding both ourselves and our partners to the highest ethical standards.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Robust Monitoring and Compliance Mechanisms:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller\'s commitment to combating modern slavery is fortified by stringent monitoring and compliance mechanisms. Suppliers must comply with our Code of Ethics, a prerequisite for collaboration with Unipuller, and are subject to periodic assessments conducted by our vigilant Compliance and Procurement teams. Noncompliance is not taken lightly, and suppliers are well aware that it can lead to contract termination.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Annually, the board conducts a thorough review of slavery and human trafficking risks within our supply chain. Despite an initial assessment indicating a very low risk, we proactively undertook further investigations. Our proactive approach included reaching out to perceived higherrisk suppliers and requiring confirmation of Modern Slavery Act compliance. The outcome of these efforts affirms that there are no concerns regarding slavery or human trafficking within Unipuller or its supply chain.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Commitment to Transparency:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This statement, as mandated by section 54(1) of the Modern Slavery Act 2015, is a testament to Unipuller\'s commitment to transparency. It serves as a comprehensive disclosure of our efforts to combat modern slavery and human trafficking for the financial year 2023.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Burhan Uddin&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chairman</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /></p>', 1, 5, 5, '2023-12-17 17:43:49', '2023-12-17 23:43:49'),
(3, 'Footer', 'About', 'statement', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At Unipuller, we are unwavering in our dedication to pioneering excellence, driving innovation, and ushering in transformative solutions within the business world. Our mission is to revolutionize industries through the introduction of cutting-edge solutions that not only meet but consistently exceed the evolving demands of businesses.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our commitment to excellence, sustainability, and a customer-centric approach forms the very essence of our existence. We are on a perpetual journey of refinement and improvement, with the singular goal of becoming the favored choice for businesses seeking reliable and innovative solutions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our team of passionate experts is resolute in driving progress and delivering exceptional value. We don\'t merely provide services; we forge strong partnerships with our clients, guiding them towards success. Together, we navigate the dynamic landscape of industry, offering solutions that are not just reliable and innovative but also precisely tailored to your unique goals and aspirations.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller is more than a service provider &ndash; we are your dedicated companion on the path to a brighter, more efficient future. Your aspirations are our fuel, and your success is our ultimate reward. Welcome to Unipuller, where your journey towards a thriving future begins.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 5, 5, '2023-12-17 17:27:48', '2023-12-17 23:27:48'),
(4, 'Footer', 'About', 'sustainability', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Unipuller unwavering commitment to sustainability is deeply woven into the fabric of our organizational culture, steering our efforts across multiple dimensions</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Environmental Responsibility:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our dedication to minimizing environmental impact extends to implementing stringent measures for carbon footprint reduction. This involves not only adopting energyefficient technologies and practices but also integrating innovative solutions for continuous improvement. Waste reduction initiatives are a cornerstone, featuring comprehensive recycling programs and responsible disposal methods. We prioritize sustainable resource management, meticulously sourcing materials and optimizing utilization to ensure minimal ecological impact.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>EcoFriendly Solutions:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In delivering business solutions, we actively integrate and champion ecofriendly technologies and practices. Our commitment transcends the immediate business context, reaching into the supply chains of our clients. By supporting and encouraging sustainable practices within these supply chains, we aim to foster a broader industry impact, influencing positive change throughout various sectors.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Community Engagement:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller goes beyond traditional business boundaries, actively engaging with local communities through a diverse range of initiatives. These include educational programs that not only impart knowledge but also focus on skill development. Additionally, we actively support social enterprises, collaborating with community leaders to identify and address local needs. Through such initiatives, we strive to ensure that our presence contributes positively to the overall wellbeing of the communities where we operate.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ethical Business Practices:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upholding the highest ethical standards is nonnegotiable for Unipuller. Our commitment to fair trade extends beyond rhetoric, becoming a core aspect of our business practices. Transparency is paramount in every stage of our operations &mdash; from sourcing to manufacturing and overall business processes &mdash; ensuring that ethical considerations are integrated seamlessly into our organizational ethos.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sustainability at Unipuller is a dynamic and evolving journey. We consistently evaluate and refine our practices, fostering a culture of innovation that seeks out the most effective solutions for minimizing environmental impact. Our teams actively explore and implement technologies that not only meet but exceed sustainability standards, demonstrating a commitment to pushing the boundaries of what is possible in environmentally conscious business practices.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Education and Advocacy:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our investment in sustainability extends to education and advocacy. We conduct comprehensive programs for employees, stakeholders, and clients, aiming not just to raise awareness but to instill a deep understanding of the importance of sustainability. Beyond internal initiatives, Unipuller plays an active role in industry events and initiatives, advocating for sustainable practices and policies that can drive positive change across the business landscape.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Measurable Goals:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller sets specific, measurable, and timebound sustainability goals aligned with international standards. Our commitment to transparency is demonstrated through regular reporting, providing stakeholders with a clear view of our progress. This transparency is a cornerstone of our accountability, allowing stakeholders to actively track and assess our sustainability commitments.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller Limited is not just a business entity; it is a catalyst for positive change. Our sustainability commitment is not a mere statement but a lived reality, manifesting through tangible actions and a comprehensive approach. We strive to address environmental, social, and ethical considerations in every facet of our operations, setting a standard for responsible corporate citizenship in the global business landscape.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /><br /></p>', 1, 5, 5, '2023-12-17 20:28:37', '2023-12-18 02:28:37'),
(5, 'Footer', 'About', 'unipullers-services', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>A Network of Expertise: Partnering for Your Success</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At Unipuller Business Solutions, we\'ve established a dynamic network of partnerships with expert thirdparty service providers, creating tailored solutions to meet your unique needs. Our collaborative approach empowers us to deliver a versatile array of services, ensuring your organization is fully prepared to excel in the everevolving business landscape.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We understand the paramount importance of dedicated expertise in various domains. To achieve this, we have established partnerships with specialist service providers in each of the following areas:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Strategic Planning:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Collaborate with seasoned experts to develop a strategic roadmap tailored to your organization\'s goals. Our partners bring indepth industry knowledge to align your business with market trends, ensuring a clear and effective path to success.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Technology Integration:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Seamlessly incorporate cuttingedge technologies into your operations with the assistance of our tech integration specialists. From cloud solutions to automation, our partners optimize your tech infrastructure for enhanced operational efficiency.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Process Optimization:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work closely with process optimization professionals to identify inefficiencies, streamline workflows, and enhance productivity. Our partners employ industry best practices to ensure your processes are finely tuned for optimal performance.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Financial Advisory:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gain invaluable insights into financial decisionmaking from our financial advisory partners. Whether it\'s investment strategies, risk management, or fiscal planning, our experts provide tailored guidance to secure your financial wellbeing.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Marketing and Branding:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Elevate your brand\'s presence with the expertise of marketing and branding specialists. Our partners craft comprehensive strategies, covering everything from digital marketing to brand positioning, ensuring your business stands out in the competitive landscape.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>IT Consulting:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Leverage technology effectively with the guidance of expert IT consultants. Our partners assess your current IT infrastructure, recommend improvements, and assist in implementing solutions that give you a competitive edge in the digital marketplace.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Human Resources Management:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Optimize your workforce with the assistance of HR management experts. From talent acquisition to employee development, our partners help create a positive workplace culture that nurtures talent and drives organizational success.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Legal and Compliance Support:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mitigate risks and ensure compliance with the help of our legal and compliance partners. They provide expert advice on regulatory matters, safeguarding your operations and reputation.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Supply Chain Management:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Enhance logistics and supply chain efficiency through partnerships with specialists. Our experts analyze your supply chain, identify optimization opportunities, and implement strategies to improve overall efficiency.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Market Research:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Stay ahead of the competition with insights from market research experts. Our partners conduct thorough market analyses, providing you with valuable data to make informed decisions and adapt to evolving market trends.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sales and Distribution Strategy:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maximize your market reach with sales and distribution strategists. Our partners develop tailored strategies to enhance your sales channels, ensuring effective distribution and increased market penetration.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Customer Relationship Management (CRM):</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build lasting connections with customers through expert CRM specialists. Our partners implement CRM systems that enhance customer satisfaction, streamline communication, and foster longterm relationships.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Business Analytics and Reporting:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Make datadriven decisions with the expertise of business analytics and reporting professionals. Our partners analyze data, providing actionable insights that contribute to better decisionmaking and improved business outcomes.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Product Development and Innovation:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Stay ahead of industry trends with innovative solutions crafted by product development and innovation specialists. Our partners bring creativity and expertise to the table, ensuring your products remain competitive and cuttingedge.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sustainability and Environmental Solutions:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Contribute to a greener future with experts in sustainability. Our partners provide solutions to meet ecofriendly standards, helping your organization adopt sustainable practices and reduce environmental impact.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Quality Control and Assurance:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ensure the highest product or service quality with collaborations with quality control and assurance professionals. Our partners implement rigorous quality control measures, ensuring customer satisfaction and compliance with industry standards.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Project Management:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Execute initiatives with precision and efficiency under the guidance of project management specialists. Our partners oversee project timelines, budgets, and resources, ensuring successful project delivery.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Training and Skill Development:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Enhance your team\'s capabilities through training and skill development experts. Our partners design programs tailored to your organizational needs, fostering continuous learning and development.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Risk Assessment and Management:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Safeguard your business against uncertainties with the help of risk assessment and management partners. Our experts identify potential risks, develop mitigation strategies, and ensure resilience in the face of challenges.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Digital Transformation:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Embrace the digital age effectively with assistance from digital transformation specialists. Our partners guide your organization through technological advancements, ensuring a seamless transition to digital processes and systems.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unipuller is dedicated to ensuring that your organization is not just prepared but primed for success, no matter the changes in the business landscape. We\'re your collaborative partner, offering a full spectrum of services by thirdparty experts to drive your achievements. With Unipuller, the path to lasting success is illuminated by expertise and innovation.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><br /><br /></p>', 1, 5, 5, '2023-12-17 20:29:13', '2023-12-18 02:29:13'),
