(17, 'Footer', 'Policies', 'privacy-and-cookies', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Safeguarding Your Personal Information: Unipuller\'s Pledge</strong></h3>\r\n<p>At Unipuller, ensuring the privacy of your data is at the core of our mission. When you use Unipuller Services, trust that your personal information is handled with utmost care.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Information Collection from Customers</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our objective is to provide outstanding products and services. Here\'s an overview of the types of information we collect:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Your Input:</strong> Anything you choose to share while using Unipuller Services. Remember, you have the choice not to provide certain information, though this may limit access to some Unipuller Services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Automated Data:</strong> Unipuller Services automatically collect and store data about your interactions and usage of our services, similar to many websites. This involves the use of cookies and unique identifiers. For a more detailed breakdown of what we collect, please refer to our data collection examples.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Information from External Sources:</strong> Occasionally, we receive information from other sources, such as updated delivery details from our carriers, ensuring accurate records and a smoother purchasing experience.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why Unipuller Processes Your Personal Information</strong></p>\r\n<p>We process your personal information for various vital purposes, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Ordering and Delivery:</strong> Your personal information is crucial for efficiently managing orders, delivering products and services, processing payments, and keeping you informed about your orders, product offers, and services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Enhancing Unipuller Services:</strong> Your data is instrumental in improving the functionality, performance, and user-friendliness of our services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Tailored Recommendations:</strong> We analyze your information to provide recommendations aligned with your interests and preferences, delivering a personalized Unipuller experience.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Voice, Image, and Camera Services:</strong> When you use voice, image, or camera services, we process your voice commands, images, videos, and other data to fulfill your requests and enhance our Unipuller services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Compliance with Legal Requirements:</strong> On certain occasions, we collect and use your personal information to meet legal obligations, such as collecting seller information for identity verification.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Effective Communication:</strong> We maintain contact with you through various channels, such as phone, email, and chat, regarding Unipuller Services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Advertising:</strong> Your personal information is invaluable for us to display ads that align with your preferences, showcasing features, products, and services tailored to you. For more details, please refer to our Interest-Based Ads notice.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Preventing Fraud and Managing Credit Risks:</strong> Personal information is used to detect and prevent fraud, ensuring the security of our customers and Unipuller. We may also employ scoring methods to assess and manage credit risks.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Consent-Based Processing:</strong> Sometimes, we may request your consent to process your personal information for specific purposes. You have the flexibility to withdraw your consent at any time.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Enhancing Your Experience with Cookies and Identifiers at Unipuller</strong></p>\r\n<p>At Unipuller, we use cookies and similar tools to enrich your shopping experience, deliver services more effectively, gain insights into your usage patterns, and present advertisements relevant to you. We\'ve also partnered with trusted third parties who use these tools alongside our ads, enabling our systems to recognize your web browser or device, ensuring you have an exceptional Unipuller experience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Does Unipuller Share Your Personal Information?</strong></p>\r\n<p>At Unipuller, we prioritize your privacy and confidentiality. Your personal information is a cornerstone of our business, and we want to assure you that we do not engage in the practice of selling our customers\' personal data to third parties. We share customer information only as described below and with Unipuller and its controlled subsidiaries that adhere to practices as protective as those described in this Privacy Notice.</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Transactions Involving Third Parties:</strong> We provide access to various services, products, applications, and skills offered by third parties through Unipuller Services. For example, you can purchase products from third-party vendors, download applications from our App Store, and enable third-party skills through our services. When such third-party transactions occur, customer personal information related to these interactions is shared with the involved third party.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Third-party Service Providers:</strong> To enhance your experience, we collaborate with other companies and individuals to perform various functions on our behalf. These functions include order fulfillment, package delivery, data analysis, marketing assistance, search results provision, payment processing, and customer service. While these third-party service providers have access to personal information required to perform their functions, they are bound by this Privacy Notice and applicable data protection laws.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In the course of our business development, we may acquire or sell other businesses or services. In such instances, customer information becomes one of the transferred assets, subject to the commitments made in any pre-existing Privacy Notice, unless the customer consents otherwise.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Protection of Unipuller and Others:</strong> We prioritize the security of your personal information. Account and personal information disclosure occurs only when necessary to comply with the law, enforce our agreements, or protect the rights, property, or safety of Unipuller, our users, or others. Such disclosures are made in line with applicable laws and regulations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Beyond these scenarios, please rest assured that you will be notified if personal information about you might be shared with third parties, and you will always have the opportunity to opt-out of such sharing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Transfers out of the European Economic Area and the UK:</strong> When we transfer personal information to countries outside the European Economic Area or the UK, we ensure that the information is transferred in compliance with this Privacy Notice and applicable data protection laws.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Securing Your Personal Information: Our Top Priority</strong></p>\r\n<p>At Unipuller, we employ multiple measures to prioritize the security of your personal information:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We use encryption protocols and software to protect the security of your personal information during transmission.</li>\r\n<li>We adhere to the Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS) when handling credit card data.</li>\r\n<li>Our physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards for collecting, storing, and disclosing personal customer information ensure the safety of your data. These security procedures may involve identity verification before disclosing personal information.</li>\r\n<li>Our devices are equipped with security features to prevent unauthorized access and data loss. You have the flexibility to customize and manage these features based on your preferences.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>To further enhance your security, it\'s important to protect against unauthorized access to your password and devices. We recommend using a unique password for your Unipuller account, distinct from other online accounts, and always remember to sign off when using a shared computer.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advertising at Unipuller:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Third-party Advertisers and Links to Other Websites:</strong> Unipuller Services may include third-party advertising and links to other websites and apps. Third-party advertising partners may collect information about you when you interact with their content and services. For detailed information about third-party advertising at Unipuller, including interest-based ads, please refer to our Interest-Based Ads notice. To adjust your advertising preferences, visit the Advertising Preferences page.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Use of Third-party Advertising Services:</strong> We provide advertising companies with information to serve you with relevant Unipuller ads and measure their effectiveness. Your name and direct identifiers are never shared in this process. Instead, we use an advertising identifier such as a cookie or a device identifier. For example, if you\'ve already downloaded one of our apps, we share your advertising identifier and event data to ensure you don\'t receive repetitive ads.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Some advertising companies may also use this information to display relevant ads from other advertisers. For guidance on opting out of interest-based advertising, please visit the Advertising Preferences page.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>What Information Can You Access with Unipuller?</strong></p>\r\n<p>With Unipuller, you have control and easy access to your personal information, such as your name, address, payment options, and more. All this can be found in the \"Your Account\" section on our website.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Choices You Have with Unipuller</strong></p>\r\n<p>Unipuller values your preferences and offers various options to tailor your experience:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Control Information Sharing:</strong> You have the choice to decide what information you provide. However, please note that not providing certain information might limit your access to some Unipuller Services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Update Your Data:</strong> You can conveniently add or modify your information on dedicated pages, and previous versions are retained for your records.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Manage Communication:</strong> Customize your communication preferences by adjusting email and in-app notification settings to your liking.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Ad Preferences:</strong> If you prefer not to see interest-based ads, you can manage your advertising preferences.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Cookies and Privacy:</strong> Learn how to manage cookies through your browser or device\'s Help feature. For a smoother experience, we recommend keeping cookies enabled.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> At Unipuller, you have the freedom to consent to or withdraw your consent for data processing at any time.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Browse Anonymously:</strong> Browsing our website without linking your activity to your account is possible by logging out and disabling cookies in your browser.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Recommendation Management:</strong> Customize your shopping experience by managing recommendations and browsing history.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Data Processing Consent:</strong> Your consent for specific data processing is respected, and you can withdraw it whenever you wish.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Device Permissions:</strong> Manage device permissions on applicable Unipuller websites, devices, or applications by referring to the appropriate settings.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Unipuller Services and Children</strong></p>\r\n<p>Unipuller is primarily designed for adults. If you are under 18, the use of Unipuller Services should involve parental or guardian supervision. We prioritize children\'s privacy, and for users under 13, please refer to our Children Privacy Notice.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Regulatory Oversight</strong></p>\r\n<p>Unipuller is firmly committed to data privacy and operates under regulatory oversight to ensure the security of your data.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Contacts, Notices, &amp; Revisions</strong></p>\r\n<p>For privacy concerns or to contact Unipuller\'s data controllers, our Customer Service is at your service. Our Privacy Notice evolves with our business, but we stand by our commitment to safeguard your data.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Children\'s Use of Unipuller Services</strong></p>\r\n<p>Unipuller Europe does not sell products intended for children. Our products are designed for purchase by adults. If you are under 18, you may only use Unipuller Services with the consent and involvement of a parent or guardian. For detailed information about how we handle personal information for Unipuller Services aimed at children under the age of 13, please consult our Children Privacy Notice.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>How Long Do We Keep Your Personal Information?</strong></p>\r\n<p>We retain your personal information to facilitate your ongoing use of Unipuller Services. This retention extends for the duration necessary to serve the pertinent purposes as outlined in this Privacy Notice. It may also be retained as required by law, such as for tax and accounting obligations, or as otherwise communicated to you. For instance, we maintain records of your transaction history to enable you to review past purchases and shipping addresses. This aids in facilitating repeat orders if desired and in enhancing the relevance of product recommendations and content.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>EU General Data Protection Regulation and UK Data Protection Laws - Legal Basis</strong></p>\r\n<p>Adherence to the EU GDPR and UK data protection laws mandates the establishment of a legal basis for our use of personal information. The chosen basis varies depending on the specific purpose for which we employ personal data. We rely on:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Performance of a contract</strong> when delivering products or services, including order handling, product delivery, and payment processing.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Our legitimate business interests</strong> and the interests of our customers when enhancing Unipuller services, detecting and preventing fraud and abuse to safeguard customer and general security, and delivering interest-based advertising.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Your consent</strong> when we request your explicit permission to process your personal information for a defined purpose. You have the prerogative to withdraw your consent at any time, after which we cease processing your data for that purpose.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Compliance with a legal obligation</strong> when personal information is used to meet legal requirements. For example, we collect seller establishment details and bank account information for identity verification.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>These and other legal bases are applied in accordance with the specific purpose of personal information usage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Contacts, Notices &amp; Revisions</strong></p>\r\n<p>If you have concerns regarding privacy at Unipuller Europe or wish to contact one of our data controllers, please reach out to our Customer Service with a comprehensive description. We are committed to resolving any issues. Additionally, our data protection officer can be contacted at <a href=\"mailto:privacy@unipuller.com\" target=\"_new\">privacy@unipuller.com</a>. You may also file a complaint with our primary supervisory authority, the Commission Nationale pour la Protection des Donn&eacute;es in Luxembourg, the Information Commissioner\'s</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Examples of Collected Information</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Details Provided When Using Unipuller Services:</strong></p>\r\n<p>You supply information when you:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Search for products or services in our stores.</li>\r\n<li>Complete orders through Unipuller Services.</li>\r\n<li>Download, stream, view, or use content via devices or related services.</li>\r\n<li>Submit information in Your Account (which may include multiple profiles for those using different email addresses or mobile numbers).</li>\r\n<li>Upload your contacts.</li>\r\n<li>Adjust settings, grant data access permissions, or engage with Unipuller devices or services.</li>\r\n<li>Submit information in your Seller Account or any other account provided for software, goods, or services development or provision to Unipuller customers.</li>\r\n<li>Present your products or services through Unipuller Services.</li>\r\n<li>Communicate with us via phone, email, or alternative means.</li>\r\n<li>Fill out questionnaires, support tickets, or contest entry forms.</li>\r\n<li>Upload or stream images, videos, or other files to Prime Photos, Unipuller Drive, or other Unipuller Services.</li>\r\n<li>Compile Playlists, Watchlists, Wish Lists, or gift registries.</li>\r\n<li>Engage in community features, provide and rate Customer Reviews.</li>\r\n<li>Specify a Special Occasion Reminder.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>As a result of these actions, you may provide us with information such as your name, address, and phone number, payment details, your age, location information, IP address, contact details of friends and others, content of reviews and emails, personal descriptions and photographs in Your Profile, images and videos stored or collected in connection with Unipuller Services, information and documents related to identity and standing, corporate and financial information, credit history data, VAT numbers, device log files, and configurations, including Wi-Fi credentials for automatic synchronization.</p>', 1, 5, 5, '2023-12-17 19:40:46', '2023-12-18 01:40:46'),
(18, 'Footer', 'Policies', 'condition-of-use-and-sale', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Welcome to Unipuller.com! Before using our services or making any purchases, please read and understand the following Terms of Use &amp; Sale. These terms govern your interaction with Unipuller.com and cover various aspects of our services, products, and your responsibilities as a user.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Terms of Use</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Electronic Communications:</strong> Your engagement with Unipuller Services involves electronic communication, and you agree that electronic communication fulfills any legal requirements for written communication.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Recommendations and Personalization:</strong> We provide personalized recommendations within Unipuller Services to enhance your experience based on your interests.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Copyright, Authors\' Rights, and Database Rights:</strong> All content on Unipuller Services is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. Unauthorized extraction or re-utilization of content is prohibited.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Trademarks:</strong> Unipuller\'s trademarks and trade dress are protected, and their use in connection with unauthorized products or services is prohibited.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>License and Access:</strong> You are granted a limited license to access and use Unipuller Services for personal and non-commercial purposes. Commercial use, data mining, or unauthorized extraction is strictly prohibited.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Your Account:</strong> Maintain the confidentiality of your account, and ensure accurate and updated information. Unipuller may terminate accounts for non-compliance with terms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Reviews, Comments, and Other Content:</strong> Users can share content, but it must adhere to guidelines. Unipuller reserves the right to edit or remove content and should be informed of defamatory or infringing content.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Intellectual Property Claims:</strong> Unipuller upholds intellectual property rights and provides procedures for reporting infringements.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Unipuller Software Terms:</strong> Additional terms apply to the use of Unipuller Software, and users must comply with these terms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Other Business:</strong> Third-party entities operate on Unipuller.com, and Unipuller is not responsible for their actions or content. Transactions with third parties are subject to their terms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Unipuller\'s Role:</strong> Unipuller facilitates third-party sales, but it is not the buyer or seller. The contract for third-party products is between the buyer and seller.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Our Liability:</strong> Unipuller strives for uninterrupted services but is not liable for losses beyond its control. Certain laws may provide additional rights.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Applicable Law:</strong> These terms are governed by the laws of the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg, with additional protections for EU or UK consumers.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Export Controls:</strong> Users agree not to export products to countries with restrictions, and Unipuller is not responsible for compliance with export restrictions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Alterations to Service or Amendments:</strong> Unipuller may make changes to services and terms, and users are bound by the terms in force during service usage.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Waiver:</strong> Unipuller retains the right to enforce rights and remedies in case of a breach of terms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Children:</strong> Unipuller does not sell products directly to children, and users under 18 should involve a parent or guardian.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Reporting of Defamatory Content on Unipuller</strong></p>\r\n<p>If you suspect defamatory content, follow the \"notice and action\" approach by notifying Unipuller through the provided channels.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Additional Unipuller Software Terms</strong></p>\r\n<p>These terms govern the use of Unipuller Software, including restrictions on integration and reverse engineering.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Conditions of Sale</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Our Agreement:</strong> Details the process of initiating a purchase, order confirmation, and dispatch confirmation. The contract is finalized upon product dispatch.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Right to Cancel:</strong> Users have the right to cancel orders within 14 days, with exceptions for certain products and services. A voluntary returns guarantee is also provided.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Pricing and Availability:</strong> Prices include VAT, and Unipuller strives to inform about product availability. Pricing verification is done before processing orders.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Product Information:</strong> Unipuller is not the manufacturer, and product information may differ from actual packaging. Unipuller is not liable for inaccuracies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Customs:</strong> Import duties and taxes may apply for deliveries outside mainland UK. Users must comply with receiving country laws.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Buy Now Ordering:</strong> Buy Now ordering is a quick and secure way to order products.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Our Liability:</strong> Unipuller is not responsible for losses not caused by a breach on its part. Some laws may grant additional rights.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Applicable Law:</strong> These conditions are governed by the laws of the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Amendments to the Conditions of Sale:</strong> Unipuller reserves the right to make changes to policies and terms.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Waiver:</strong> Unipuller\'s rights and remedies remain enforceable in case of a breach.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Children:</strong> Unipuller does not sell products for children; adult involvement is advised.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Read these terms carefully before using Unipuller Services. Your continued use indicates agreement with these terms.</p>', 1, 5, 5, '2023-12-17 20:33:57', '2023-12-18 02:33:57'),
(19, 'Footer', 'Policies', 'returns-and-refund-policies', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Returns Policy Overview</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Unipuller.com, together with numerous sellers, facilitates the return of most items within 30 days from the delivery date. This document outlines the return policies, providing specific procedures for various scenarios. Refunds for items shipped by Unipuller are completed within a maximum of 14 days, accompanied by an automated email confirmation. Extended refund periods may apply under certain circumstances, with the refund expected to appear in the customer\'s bank account or credit card statement within a maximum of 7 business days. Comprehensive details about the refund policy are accessible in the Refunds section or through customer services.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Enhancing the Shopping Experience:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Unipuller.com strives to guarantee a positive shopping experience. Customers retain the right to cancel most item purchases within 14 days, and statutory rights are applicable for goods not meeting the described criteria, unfit for purpose, or lacking satisfactory quality.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mistaken Returns:</strong> When initiating a return, it is crucial to include the precise and complete item. If an error leads to dispatching the wrong item, promptly contact Customer Service. Unipuller does not store mistakenly sent items, and no compensation is provided for inaccurately dispatched items.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Statutory Cancellation Right:</strong> Customers possess the statutory entitlement to cancel orders for any reason within 14 days of receiving the item. Guidelines for canceling orders are outlined in clause 2 of the Conditions of Use &amp; Sale on the Returns Support Centre.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Voluntary Returns Policy:</strong> In addition to statutory cancellation rights, the majority of unused and undamaged products can be returned within 30 days. Initiate returns through the Returns Support Centre, ensuring items are maintained in their original condition.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Returns Guarantee Exclusions:</strong> Certain products are exempt from the Returns Guarantee, encompassing items unsuitable for return due to health protection or hygiene, sealed audio/video recordings, personalized items, perishables, and more.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Returns Costs &amp; Methods:</strong> Unipuller guarantees the refund of return costs for items sold or dispatched by Unipuller, with specific exclusions. Return methods and costs vary, ranging from drop-off services, Heavy-Bulky options, Lockers, Hub Counters, to label-free returns via QR code.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Post-30-Day Resolution for Defective Items:</strong> For defects beyond 30 days, customers are urged to explore troubleshooting on the Product Support Help page. Unipuller addresses defects through repairs, replacements, or refunds for qualifying items. Returns are not accepted after 30 days for consumable products or defects resulting from accidental damage, deliberate harm, external factors, or normal wear and tear.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Unipuller Global Store, Fresh Items, Handmade, Customized, and Luxury Stores:</strong> Detailed return information is provided for each category, emphasizing conditions, methods, and exceptions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Specific Details for Various Products:</strong> Instructions for returning specific items, such as those sold and dispatched by a Seller on Unipuller Marketplace, Prime Video, Unipuller Music, Kindle, Unipuller Appstore for Android, Unipuller Games and Software downloads, AutoRip Music, Shoes, Clothing, Jewelry &amp; Watches, items containing Hazardous Materials, and Very High Value Items, are accessible on Unipuller\'s website.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Contact Information:</strong> For postal correspondence, customers can reach Unipuller Ltd at 1 Gunthorpe Street, Unit 1, Nagpal House, E1 1RG, London, UK. However, this address is not for returns, which should be processed through the Returns Support Centre. For quicker responses, it\'s advisable to visit Customer Service.</p>', 1, 5, 5, '2023-12-17 20:34:39', '2023-12-18 02:34:39'),
